import React from "react";
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom';
import Footer from "./compoent/Footer"
import DoctorDashboard from "./compoent/DoctorDashboard"
import DoctorProfile from "./compoent/DoctorProfile"
import AppointmentList from "./compoent/AppointmentList"
import AppointmentCard from "./compoent/AppointmentCard"
import AppointmentDetails from "./compoent/AppointmentDetails"
import AppointmentActions from "./compoent/AppointmentActions"


function Routes() {
  return (
    <>
      <Router>
      <DoctorDashboard />
        <Switch>
            <Route path='/doctorprofile' compoent={DoctorProfile} exact>
            <DoctorProfile />
            </Route>
              <Route path='/appointmentlist' compoent={AppointmentList} exact>
            <AppointmentList />
            </Route>
             <Route path='/appointmentcard' compoent={AppointmentCard} exact>
            <AppointmentCard />
            </Route>
             <Route path='/appointmentdetails' compoent={AppointmentDetails} exact>
            <AppointmentDetails />
            </Route>
            <Route path='/appointmentactions' compoent={AppointmentActions} exact>
            <AppointmentActions />
            </Route>
        </Switch>
      </Router>
    </>
  )
}

export default Routes
